# boolean-multiple-trailing-spaces

## Input

```
a true   
b false   

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..21
  ENTRY@0..10
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    BOOLEAN@2..6
      TRUE@2..6 "true"
    SPACE@6..9 "   "
    NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
  ENTRY@10..21
    WORD_KEY@10..11
      WORD@10..11 "b"
    SPACE@11..12 " "
    BOOLEAN@12..17
      FALSE@12..17 "false"
    SPACE@17..20 "   "
    NEWLINE@20..21 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: Boolean {
                token: TRUE@2..6 "true",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@10..11 "b",
            },
            value: Boolean {
                token: FALSE@12..17 "false",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

